@startuml CurrentPrototype
title Current Prototype Architecture

skinparam shadowing false
skinparam componentStyle rectangle

actor User

package "Frontend" {
    rectangle "Web UI\n(React)" as UI
}

package "Backend Services" {
    rectangle "REST API\n(FastAPI)" as API
    database "PostgreSQL" as DB
    rectangle "NATS\nJetStream" as NATS
}

package "Worker" {
    rectangle "Job Worker\n(Python)" as JobWorker
}

package "Execution" {
    rectangle "Docker\nContainers" as Docker
    folder "Checkpoints" as Checkpoints
}

' Interactions
User --> UI : submit/stop/resume
UI --> API : HTTP
API --> DB : job state
API --> NATS : publish events
NATS --> JobWorker : subscribe
JobWorker --> Docker : run containers
Docker --> Checkpoints : save/load

note right of API
    • Job CRUD
    • Stop/Resume
    • Image upload
end note

note right of JobWorker
    • FIFO queue
    • Single job at a time
    • Event-driven
    • State reconciliation
    
    → Evolves to: Scheduler + K8s Actuator
end note

note right of Docker
    • Signal handling
    • Checkpointing
    • Resumable execution
    
    → Evolves to: K8s Jobs / Pods
    → Docker CLI → Kubernetes API
end note

note right of Checkpoints
    → Evolves to: S3 (distributed storage)
end note

@enduml
